Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:39.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times, he'll use his spiritual\npowers to help people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At others, he'll use his Wind Tunnel\nto subjugate demons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:48.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In orderto destroy our\narch-enemy Naraku,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku journeys\ntogetherwith us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:54.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He seems to love women\nand making money,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:58.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but at critical times,\nhe's very dependable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:09.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall be off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:14.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterMonk, thank you so\nmuch for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now we can live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:20.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You saved ourvillage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:23.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No such thing! I only did what\nhad to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:25.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:28.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterMonk! Please tell us your\nname at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:32.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:52.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lately, we only sleep\nin the open fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:55.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How I long for a good night's sleep with\na roof over ourheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:58.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Look! Avillage!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:02:59.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll be able to sleep\nindoors tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:07.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps we'll get news\nabout Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:10.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All nice and clean now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! T-That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:27.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:32.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Miroku!\NHe's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:33.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- "Miroku is coming"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You corrupt monk!\NHow dare you deceive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,J-Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:48.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't act innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No need fortalk!\NGet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on, Miroku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, that's a difficult question\nto answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do?\NThere're so many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:18.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At times like this, before\nanyone is injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the only thing to do\nis run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:22.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what that was\nall about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:31.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It concerns Miroku, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He probably did some mischief\nin the past there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:37.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But they sure were angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you do, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:45.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well...\NNo sense thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You probably can't remember\nall the bad things you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:00.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Surrounded by beautiful women\nand partying it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:03.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that's a memory\NI wouldn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you bear my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bearyour child,\nso drink up, MasterMonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Drink it all up, monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:23.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay then... I'll down it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! Anothervillage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tonight for sure...\NI'll get a good night's sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterMonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?!\N- What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear...\NWhat is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:01.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You promised I could bear\nyour child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:06.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to bear his child!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I see... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, let's take turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:11.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:15.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have some nerve\ncoming back here, you fake monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't think you'll get away\nscot-free!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:22.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear... This doesn't look\ngood at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:26.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's get away\nfrom here, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why're you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:32.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why must we run away, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:36.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think you should humbly apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be so heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:42.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, you sowed these seeds\nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you'd bettertake\nresponsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you, I!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Shippo!\NYou understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:56.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm just a kid. I don't understand\nthis grown-up stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me, Miroku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please hearme out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to keep it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:10.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Women are frightening creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:11.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- No, nothing.\N- No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:19.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So just what did Miroku do\nin this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd have to hearit to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:29.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so, this person\nbuilt a fine storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, he had so many worries...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:35.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would robbers break in? Would\na fire break out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And thus, this sutra charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wards off evil spirits,\npromotes good health,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,protects the home,\nensures safe birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:50.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This sutra charm will take care\nof every need and concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Furthermore!\NFor a limited time only,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll give you two\nforthe price of one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:59.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a little suspicious\nabout this charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Usually, a safe-delivery charm\nis for childbirth only.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:08.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what makes this charm\nso wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:12.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That anyone would complain\nabout its multiple benefits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What if an evil spirit has\na safe delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't have it get healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:22.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This despicable monk tricked us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:26.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,into buying worthless charms\nat exorbitant prices!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you ended up buying them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh... Monk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:44.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't you stop eating and\nbegin the exorcism?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Evil spirit begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:58.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:11.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}T- That's all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:16.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At my house, he made us feel beholden\nwith his {\i1}fake{\i0} exorcism,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then ate and slept like there\nwas no tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:26.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Every time he came to the village,\nhe flirted with the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterMonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- How nice! How nice!\N- This way! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry, come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:40.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he really a high-ranking monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks to him,\nall the girls are... Look foryourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:49.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh Miroku... Even under arrest,\nyou're so divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and release Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well... It's no different from\nhow Miroku always acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:58.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he's neverbeen\nthis popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're wrong about that, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wrong about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:06.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, you're wrong about\nme not being so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:10.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's even more wrong\nthat I'm tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:12.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:17.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the first time\NI've been to this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop your lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can you look so smug\nand lie before all these witnesses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's the truth, so I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:36.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yesterday and now today...\nall lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can you tell such bold-faced lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:39.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's throw him in the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:43.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:45.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He just said,\N"yesterday and now today."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:54.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yesterday and today... Miroku has\nbeen with us all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:57.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You finally understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:06.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then just who was\nthis other Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:14.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, so you are the famous\NMasterMiroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:17.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, MasterMiroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing in\na village like ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:23.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:26.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was passing nearthis village\nduring my journey
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:29.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I felt a very\nsuspicious aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you did, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are amazing, Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:40.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That you would sense the presence\nof the demon from the outskirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:44.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then we must ask you to\nexterminate the demon immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:50.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? It looked for a second that\nyou grew bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:54.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh... err... it must be\nyourimagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Afake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:06.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone is using my identity and\nis up to no good in this region.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why must you look at me\nlike that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:13.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Think about it...\NThat's the only explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- But...\N- I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What good does it do\nto impersonate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:23.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd pick someone else to\nimpersonate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:27.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I'm suggesting\nthat we check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you all babbling about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Throw him in the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:33.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,J-Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We understand how you feel,\nbut this man denies it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:39.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can throw him in the river\nafterwe learn the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:46.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well whatever! Just untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't try to talk your way\noutta this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're someone else,\nshow us proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:59.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! Will you cut\nall this racket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:05.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you insist that Miroku\nis guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then YOU show us proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:11.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why's he so rough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew you'd say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then we'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:22.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Has he finally lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:36.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see. So that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have unraveled the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:44.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But... in that position...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He doesn't look too convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:50.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I keep asking you...\nto untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The impostor is heading\nforthe next village!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:03.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who is this impostor, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:08.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll see when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:11.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He knows me well\nand can imitate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:15.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That leaf gave him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:24.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, MasterMiroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:29.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's a shrine deep\nin this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:35.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A raccoon dog demon now\nhaunts the interior of the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh well... A raccoon dog should\nlisten to reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'd be okay if it kept to\nfeeding on mountain prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:46.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But now it attacks our\nlivestock and fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:50.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With the illustrious Miroku here,\nwe're not too worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But please do be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:55.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're here, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:06.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:08.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That must be the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No need to worry.\NIt's just a raccoon dog, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:26.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What does a mortal want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:30.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you ARE a raccoon dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a weasel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:36.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You look like a raccoon dog to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:42.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although, I love eating raccoon dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:43.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really human?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:49.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:52.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You smell like a vermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:57.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:03.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if I do say so myself,\NI am a famous monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one that uses the Wind Tunnel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:10.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you apologize now,\NI shall forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is an opportune time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:20.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall devour you and become\nthe most powerful demon in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Why's Miroku here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:35.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is supposed\nto be in the cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Let's hurry!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:51.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you ARE a raccoon dog!\NI'll turn you into stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:04.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:08.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come any closer, and I'll\nuncovermy Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You're bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:14.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall I show you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... But you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...back to being... a raccoon dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No-o-o-o-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:31.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid raccoon dog.\NSay your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:35.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I promise to stop this!\NPlease forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never forget those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:39.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterMiroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:58.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! You're the raccoon dog's partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you... raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:02.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said I'm a weasel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:04.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Justgo back quietly\nto yourmountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:11.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate violence.\NSo let's be civil about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:16.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! You're all raccoon dogs!\NDon't talk big!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll make stew outta all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:23.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess he doesn't understand reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:35.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it! He's the REAL Miroku,\nafter all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:42.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!\NForgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Please, oh please, stop!\N- As long as you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? It's all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Must be a weak raccoon dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:55.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not a raccoon dog, a weasel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said I'm a weasel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:02.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, don't try anything\nbad from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yesss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:11.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as you understand.\NNow go back to your mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:14.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:22.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want a full explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you impersonate\NMiroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ljust decided on the\nspur of the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:37.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was so hungry,\NI couldn't bearit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:41.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I impersonated Miroku\njust for one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:43.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it went well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yes! It went\nunbelievably well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:49.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you started liking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:53.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen here, Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:54.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:56.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you've learned yourlesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:59.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,don't try anything foolish\nlike this ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:04.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The trouble I went through\nall because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:05.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:08.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I really did impersonate you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:14.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I neverdid anything\nto disparage you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How disrespectful of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that how you see me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:25.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I really tried my utmost\nto pretend to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How you acted wasn't any different\nfrom how Miroku would act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How rude of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:37.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only thing different is that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hachiemon was more\nthe lady's man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:47.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can you teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Teach you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:55.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The secret to being popular\nwith the girls... What else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:21:01.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well sir... Indifference ensures success.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Indifference?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:08.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! What are you two\nwhispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:09.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You probably have\nlecherous ideas again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:15.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:21.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does my face look like I have\nsuch thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:27.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:28.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:34.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:39.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Let's go!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:44.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up!\NMiroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:48.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the real Miroku.\NYou can talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:52.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!\NHe's the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:55.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop fooling around,\nyou trickstermonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:58.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You womanizer!\NYou lecher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:00.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You crook! You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:02.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:04.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what are you up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Indifference, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:07.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's impossible for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:51.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did that demon have\na fake Sacred Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:53.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone gave it to him.
